        "title": "Draw app",
        "excerpt":"  Transcript “Draw” is one of the sample apps in Fizzygum. To open it, double click on the paint bucket:   The window has a toolbar and the “editing pencil” is highlighted. When clicked, the toolbar is hidden, for less clutter:   Click again to use the toolbar:   You can use it as a traditional drawing application:   The Draw app accepts any drop, and the dropped items will leave a stamp:   That’s it for the “draw” app, check out the other documents to see how to easily customise what the drawing tools do. ","categories": [],
